  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.164,
    "endTime": 24.0,
    "text": "This is a hard question."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.0,
    "endTime": 25.605,
    "text": "How they work all day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.605,
    "endTime": 27.963,
    "text": "Why they're always tired when they wake up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.963,
    "endTime": 29.392,
    "text": "How they snore loud."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.392,
    "endTime": 31.192,
    "text": "That they sleep too long."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.193,
    "endTime": 32.835,
    "text": "They're just so sophisticated."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.835,
    "endTime": 35.2,
    "text": "Why they always say, like, \"Hey, baby.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.2,
    "endTime": 36.835,
    "text": "Why do they call them baby?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.835,
    "endTime": 44.1,
    "text": "I don't understand why grown-ups have to do everything so fast and quickly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.1,
    "endTime": 45.300000000000004,
    "text": "It's kind of boring."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.3,
    "endTime": 48.4,
    "text": "What is something you don't understand about grown-ups?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.4,
    "endTime": 52.205,
    "text": "That sometimes they're kind of awkward."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.205,
    "endTime": 54.104,
    "text": "Why they do taxes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.104,
    "endTime": 56.842999999999996,
    "text": "They don't like playing video games with you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.843,
    "endTime": 60.300000000000004,
    "text": "They always get the bigger room with a bathroom, and I have to go to another bathroom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.3,
    "endTime": 64.342,
    "text": "What's something you don't understand about grown-ups?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.342,
    "endTime": 65.703,
    "text": "Why they like beer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.703,
    "endTime": 66.854,
    "text": "Why do they get drunk?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.854,
    "endTime": 71.382,
    "text": "When they drink vodka mixed with stuff, and they think it tastes good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.382,
    "endTime": 74.489,
    "text": "When they think that beer and stuff is essential."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.489,
    "endTime": 75.322,
    "text": "They smoke."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.322,
    "endTime": 76.34100000000001,
    "text": "They like coffee."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.341,
    "endTime": 77.726,
    "text": "How they like coffee."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.727,
    "endTime": 79.5,
    "text": "Why they drink coffee."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.5,
    "endTime": 81.878,
    "text": "It tastes terrible."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.878,
    "endTime": 84.569,
    "text": "How they do so much stuff, like cook everything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.569,
    "endTime": 86.147,
    "text": "And I don't even know how to cook."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.147,
    "endTime": 90.31400000000001,
    "text": "I don't know why kids make German cakes with them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.848,
    "endTime": 93.39,
    "text": "Why they like spicy food."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.39,
    "endTime": 95.0,
    "text": "Why they like stealing all my ice cream."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.0,
    "endTime": 97.996,
    "text": "They eat way more than I do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.996,
    "endTime": 100.048,
    "text": "Why they always have to go on a diet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.049,
    "endTime": 102.27000000000001,
    "text": "Yeah. I don't know why mom eats so many vegetables."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.27,
    "endTime": 104.841,
    "text": "She's trying to be healthy. So boring."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.841,
    "endTime": 106.378,
    "text": "Why they don't eat sugar."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.379,
    "endTime": 107.32900000000001,
    "text": "Gummies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.329,
    "endTime": 109.398,
    "text": "They get to drink soda."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.398,
    "endTime": 112.0,
    "text": "And eat ice cream all night and I don't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.0,
    "endTime": 114.721,
    "text": "If they say it's so bad, why do they do it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.721,
    "endTime": 117.512,
    "text": "Why can't the kids do that at night?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.512,
    "endTime": 120.0,
    "text": "When you ask somebody can I get candy? No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.0,
    "endTime": 121.443,
    "text": "They don't say yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.443,
    "endTime": 122.39,
    "text": "They'll say no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.39,
    "endTime": 124.0,
    "text": "Why they always say no?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.0,
    "endTime": 126.102,
    "text": "They tell us to do things."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.102,
    "endTime": 126.935,
    "text": "Why are they so-"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.935,
    "endTime": 127.4,
    "text": "Bossy?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.4,
    "endTime": 129.752,
    "text": "Why do they always have to be so demanding?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.752,
    "endTime": 135.965,
    "text": "It can be the slightest thing, like they're missing sunscreen, like right here, just one little dot, and they have to put it on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.965,
    "endTime": 137.803,
    "text": "I just don't get that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.803,
    "endTime": 140.494,
    "text": "Why they can be in control of everything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.494,
    "endTime": 143.231,
    "text": "Why they pester us to clean our rooms."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.231,
    "endTime": 144.881,
    "text": "They be mean to me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.881,
    "endTime": 147.273,
    "text": "Why they have weird mood swings."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.273,
    "endTime": 148.442,
